&lt;p&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.rceb.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Regional Center&amp;nbsp;of the East Bay (RCEB)&lt;/a&gt; is one of 21 Regional Centers that are community-based, private non-profit corporations under contract with the California Department of Developmental Services.&amp;nbsp;RCEB&amp;nbsp;provides intake, assessment, diagnosis, and coordinates community-based services for over 25,000 children and adults with developmental disabilities in Alameda and Contra Costa counties.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
