&lt;li&gt;Back-up for Secretary in the event of vacation, leave, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data Processing for the Intake &amp;amp; Assessment Unit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintains and reports the stats and logs for the Intake &amp;amp; Assessment Unit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assists in finding interpreters for assessments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Creates and edits forms as requested.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Type various reports and composes letters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scans and sends closed files to the Records Technician.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Answers phones and direct calls, greets visitors, performs word processing, filing, scanning, and faxing.&lt;/li&gt;
